                        <interp inst="t18450407-name-928" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS WITHERS</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic"> policeman.</hi>) I apprehended the prisoner—I found on him this duplicate for a book.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
